## APPENDIX B: REPORT LIMITATIONS

This report is based solely on the artifacts identified in the brief provided to the due diligence team: `UsersController.scala` (Scala 3/sbt) and `acquisition-plan.md`. It does not constitute a complete technical due diligence assessment and should not be relied upon as such. Conclusions regarding production systems, full codebase quality, infrastructure security, and engineering process maturity are necessarily qualified pending expanded access as outlined in the due diligence timeline (January 15 – March 15).

The due diligence team has not independently verified the accuracy of claims regarding SOC 2 Type II or HIPAA certification, ARR, customer relationships, headcount, or patent validity. All such claims require independent verification through the processes described herein.

